{
  "texts": [
    "Despite these strengths, LLMs often face challenges in accurately retrieving information, particularly when dealing with complex or contextually complex queries, and the reliability of LLMs in discerning factual correctness and contextual appropriateness has been a subject of ongoing research [6], [7].",
    "Studies have shown that while LLMs excel in generating coherent and contextually relevant responses, they occasionally falter in ensuring the factual accuracy and specificity required in high-stakes scenarios [8], [6], [9].",
    "This limitation underlines the need for innovative approaches to enhance the information retrieval mechanisms within LLMs, paving the way for the integration of additional cognitive strategies like symbolic reasoning [10].",
    "Research ObjectiveThe primary objective of this research is to enhance the information retrieval capabilities of TinyLlama, a 1.1 billion parameter LLM, through the integration of deep learning and symbolic reasoning techniques.",
    "By doing so, this study aims to address the existing limitations in accuracy and context-awareness observed in LLMs, specifically focusing on the retrieval of information without the need for human intervention or validation."
  ]
}